        <h1>Text Instructions</h1>
        <h3>Getting started</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Head over to the <a href="https://github.com/dradis/dradis-ce">Dradis Framework repo</a> on GitHub.</li>
          <li>On your local system, run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ git clone https://github.com/dradis/dradis-ce.git</code><br/><code>$ cd dradis-ce/</code></li>
          <li>Run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ bundle install</code></li>
          <li>Run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ ./bin/setup</code></li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="bullet two-col-bullet">
      <div class="bullet-content" style="margin-left: 0">
